# Kaiwa Scheduled Jobs
# Format: minute hour day month weekday command
#
# Send daily reminder emails at 9 AM UTC every day
0 9 * * * curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $CRON_SECRET" "https://trykaiwa.com/api/cron/send-reminders"

# Example: Run at 9 AM Pacific (5 PM UTC) every day
# 0 17 * * * curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $CRON_SECRET" "https://trykaiwa.com/api/cron/send-reminders"
